dc_title_s: Roads and ROW Grant County, WI 2021
dc_description_s: This data represents roads and Right of Ways (ROW) for Grant County, Wisconsin in 2021. [Roads: Road centerlines for Grant County, Wisconsin. Digitized from Wisconsin aerial imagery and developed for emergency mapping. Attributes are based on NENA standards and are MSAG valid where applicable.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most recent version of this data, please visit: http://www.grantcountylandrecords.com/publicinfo/
